{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Tips Menggambar Komik Chibi Dari Author Emma&#8217;s Ghost Diary","content":"<p>Web comic semakin mendapat tempat dan perhatian penggemar komik dunia. Termasuk di negara kita Indonesia.</p>\n<p>Rasanya mudah untuk menemukan web comic di internet yang dibuat atau diciptakan oleh orang Indonesia. Baik itu melalui portal web comic terkemuka seperti CIAYO Comics maupun tempat-tempat lain seperti website pribadi ataupun media sosial. Di Facebook, Twitter serta di Instagram misalnya; ada lusinan karya web comic yang bersaing untuk merebut atensi pembaca komik.</p>\n<p>Dengan berbagai jenis model gambar dan tema, para komikus web comic Indonesia ini merupakan pemain penting perkembangan web comic secara nyata di jagad komik digital Indonesia sekarang.</p>\n<p>Salah satu jenis dan metode gambar web comic buatan Indonesia yang populer dan memiliki basis penggemar besar adalah model gambar chibi alias imut <em>petite</em>. Model gambar seperti ini misalnya seperti yang di adopsi oleh pengarang web comic “<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Deathwindow/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Emma’s Ghost Diary</a>” yang populer di media sosial Facebook.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50794\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50794\" data-attachment-id=\"50794\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/01-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50794\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Deskgram\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50794\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Deskgram</p></div></p>\n<p>Perkenalkan <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kerbo.medan\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Deswondo Efarys Radlika</a>, alias “Deathwindow”. Pria ramah bertubuh bongsor ini menciptakan konsep “Emma” sejak lama, yaitu sejak tahun 2011. Saat itu format, proporsi maupun eksekusi konsep Emma berbeda dengan yang sekarang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50795\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50795\" data-attachment-id=\"50795\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/02-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50795\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"Deathwindow. Sumber: Harry Rezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50795\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Deathwindow. Sumber: Harry Rezqiano</p></div></p>\n<p>“Di tahun 2010 saya menciptakan komik berjudul ‘Pacarku Kuntilanak’ yang ber-genre romansa horor” terang Deathwindow saat ditanya sejarah IP ciptaannya. “Desain karakter dan plot di kisah itu kemudian melebar dan terciptalah <em>spin-off</em> berjudul ‘Emma’ dari situ. Yang akhirnya jadi seri yang berdiri sendiri hingga sekarang” tambahnya kemudian.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50796\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50796\" data-attachment-id=\"50796\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/03-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50796\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"Desain awal tahun 2010. Sumber: Deathwindow Pro\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50796\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain awal tahun 2010. Sumber: Deathwindow Pro</p></div></p>\n<p>Desain di ‘Pacarku Kuntilanak’ saat itu belum terlalu mengadopsi gaya gambar chibi yang imut seperti yang bisa dilihat saat ini di ‘Emma’. Gaya gambar chibi baru mulai dilakukan oleh Deathwindow sejak fokus ke Emma di tahun 2011.</p>\n<p>Alasannya karena waktu itu terlihat belum banyak yang mengadopsi gaya gambar chibi. Tema cerita juga diubah. Dari ‘romansa horor’ diubah menjadi ‘komedi harian yang dialami makhluk halus khas (daerah Medan) Indonesia’.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50797\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50797\" data-attachment-id=\"50797\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/04-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-50797 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"emma's ghost diary\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50797\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Desain chibi makhluk halus (ki-ka) Genderuwo, Jin, Jin, Ifrit, Jin &amp; Hantu Noni Belanda. Sumber: Deathwindow Pro</p></div></p>\n<p>Perubahan-perubahan yang terjadi ternyata dapat diterima dengan baik oleh publik pembaca “Pacarku Kuntilanak” sebelumnya. Web comic “Emma’s Ghost Diary” memiliki banyak penggemar di media sosial dimana dia dimuat, yaitu di Facebook dan Instagram.</p>\n<p>Gaya gambar chibi di Emma dipelajari dan diterapkan Deathwindow seiring waktu sejak konsepnya mulai baku di tahun 2011. Karakter-karakter yang ada digambarkan secara <em>cartoonish</em>, chibi dan secara general memiliki proporsi tubuh yang imut.</p>\n<p>Bagaimana Deathwindow menggambarnya?</p>\n<h3>Mengemas Ide Komik 4koma Dengan Cara Unik</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50798\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50798\" data-attachment-id=\"50798\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/05-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50798\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: Deathwindow Pro\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50798\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Deathwindow Pro</p></div></p>\n<p>Web comic Emma’s Ghost Diary mengadopsi konsep “yon-koma” atau “komik empat panel”. Model ini merupakan model yang paling sering digunakan untuk komik dengan genre komedi. Jangan menganggap konsep komik empat panel itu mudah karena aslinya tidak gampang menciptakan satu situasi/adegan yang ‘mulai sampai selesai’ hanya dalam empat penggambaran. Perlu ada kekuatan bercerita yang seimbang antara narasi dengan grafis.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50799\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50799\" data-attachment-id=\"50799\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/06-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50799\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"Model komik empat panel atau yon-koma. Sumber: Deskgram\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50799\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Model komik empat panel atau yon-koma. Sumber: Deskgram</p></div></p>\n<p>Menurut Deathwindow, ide cerita dari Emma selalu muncul dari situasi yang dia lihat/baca/alami sehari-hari.</p>\n<p><strong>Ide tersebut langsung dia gambarkan dalam bentuk sketsa di kertas dengan empat panel kotak yang biasa dia bawa dalam tas.</strong> Namun saat ide datang dan kertas gambar itu tidak tersedia, dia akan menciptakan sebuah sketsa kasar di buku atau kertas yang ada.</p>\n<p><strong>“Intinya ide yang datang jangan sampai lepas. Harus ter-visualkan di atas bidang gambar” papar Deathwindow saat ditanya soal kemungkinan sebuah ide bisa terlupakan.</strong></p>\n<h3>Cara Author Emma&#8217;s Ghost Diary Menggambar Komik 4koma Chibi</h3>\n<p>Deathwindow mencoba memperlihatkan cara dia menciptakan satu yon-koma dari Emma’s Ghost Diary.</p>\n<p>Setelah ide yang mau digambarkan sudah <em>fix</em>, selanjutnya adalah mulai ‘memecah’ ide tadi agar dapat mengalir lewat empat kotak. Deathwindow memiliki kebiasaan (atau menurut saya “<em>personal skill”</em>) dimana dia langsung menggambar ide dengan format ‘gambar jadi’. Dalam artian dia jarang melakukan pembuatan ‘kerangka karakter’ yang berbentuk garis-garis ataupun bulatan-bulatan. Bukan berarti dia tidak pernah melakukan hal itu sama sekali; karena menurutnya sendiri kadang-kadang dia membuat konsep dalam bentuk ‘stickman’ untuk mem-visualkan ide ke atas kertas.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50800\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50800\" data-attachment-id=\"50800\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/07-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50800\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"Langkah pertama. Gunakan pensil, kertas dan imajinasi. Sumber: Harry Rezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50800\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Langkah pertama. Gunakan pensil, kertas dan imajinasi. Sumber: Harry Rezqiano</p></div></p>\n<p>“Tapi saya lebih sering mencoba menggambar langsung karakter dan situasi yang jadi ide yon-koma dalam bentuk gambar jadi” paparnya saat men-demonstrasikan mekanisme membuat komik chibi Emma-nya.</p>\n<p>Deathwindow menganut mekanisme bekerja dengan sistem <em>hybrid</em>: percampuran antara manual dengan digital. Dia lebih suka menggambar konsep komiknya di atas kertas dengan pensil dan pena gambar ketimbang menggambar menggunakan tablet grafis.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50801\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50801\" data-attachment-id=\"50801\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/08-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/08-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-emma&#8217;s-ghost-diary\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/08-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/08-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50801\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/08-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" alt=\"Langkah kedua. Visualkan ide dengan aliran cerita. Sumber: Harry Rezqiano\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/08-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/08-emmas-ghost-diary-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50801\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Langkah kedua. Visualkan ide dengan aliran cerita. Sumber: Harry Rezqiano</p></div></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50802\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50802\" data-attachment-id=\"50802\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/chit-chat/emmas-ghost-diary-menggambar-komik-chibi/attachment/09-emmas-ghost-diary/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/09-emmas-ghost-diary.jpg\" data-or